(64, 'Front Desk Officer', 'Consulting', 'BACHELOR DEGREE', '1 - 3 years', '45', '', 'Sokoto ', '', 'Full time', '1733387324_front desk officer vacancy image.jpg', 'Professional', 'Attractive', '2024-12-30', '<p>The Front Desk Officer serves as the first point of contact for visitors and clients, providing a warm and professional welcome. This role is essential in ensuring smooth and efficient operations at the front desk, managing administrative tasks, and supporting overall office functionality.</p>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>BSC/HND in any field plus 1-year minimum experience in customer care management, marketing/sales experience, relationship management, and related field.</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to speak Hausa language is an added advantage.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Provide a friendly and professional greeting to all visitors and clients.</li>\r\n	<li>Answer and direct incoming phone calls promptly and courteously.</li>\r\n	<li>Handle inquiries and provide information as needed.</li>\r\n	<li>Perform general administrative duties such as filing, photocopying, and data entry.</li>\r\n	<li>Receive, sort, and distribute incoming mail and packages.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure all necessary materials (e.g., brochures, forms) are available and up-to-date.</li>\r\n	<li>Address and resolve visitor and client inquiries and complaints in a professional manner.</li>\r\n	<li>Provide information and assistance as required.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2024-12-05', 'aolayande@icsoutsourcing.com', 'approved'),
(65, 'Recruitment Officer', 'Automobile', 'BACHELOR DEGREE', '3 - 5 years', '45', '', 'Sokoto ', '', 'Full time', 'RO IMAGE.avif', 'Professional', 'Attractive', '2024-12-30', '<p>To develop and implement recruitment strategies, source candidates through a variety of channels, including online job boards, social media, and networking events.</p>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Minimum of Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Human Resources, Business Administration, or a related field. CIPM is an added advantage.</li>\r\n	<li>Minimum of 3-5 years of experience in a recruiting or related field preferred.</li>\r\n	<li>Experience with Applicant Tracking Systems (ATS) and other software.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Screening and interviewing candidates.</li>\r\n	<li>Making job offers to successful candidates.</li>\r\n	<li>Maintaining up-to-date records of all candidates and applications.</li>\r\n	<li>Analyzing recruitment data and metrics to identify trends and areas for improvement.</li>\r\n	<li>Working closely with the Recruitment &amp; Selection team to ensure a smooth and efficient recruitment process.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2024-12-05', 'aolayande@icsoutsourcing.com', 'approved'),
(66, 'Business Development Officer', 'Banking & Finance', 'HND, BACHELOR', '3 - 5 years', '45', '', 'Nationwide', '', 'Full time', 'business development officer.avif', 'Professional', 'Attractive', '2024-12-30', '<p>Our client is seeking an experienced Business Development professional with a background in SME banking/lending and a<br />\r\nproven track record of deal flow particularly in the retail and healthcare sectors for a contract position. The successful<br />\r\ncandidate will be primarily responsible for identifying new business opportunities and loans, building relationships, and<br />\r\ndriving growth&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Minimum 3 years of work experience in SME banking/lending, underwriting, sales, or business development<br />\r\nwithin the financial services industry.<br />\r\nâ— Minimum of a Higher National Diploma (HND) in a related field (e.g., finance, business, economics)<br />\r\nâ— Proven track record of successfully sourcing and closing business loans, particularly in the retail and<br />\r\nhealthcare sectors.<br />\r\nâ— Ability to work independently and as part of a team in a fast-paced, dynamic environment as well as meet<br />\r\ndeadlines<br />\r\nâ— Strong analytical skills and attention to detail.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are the best-fit candidate for this role, please send CV with BDO as a subject to resourcing@icsoutsourcing.com</p>\r\n', '<p>Identify and pursue new business opportunities in the SME sector, particularly in retail and healthcare<br />\r\nâ— Develop and maintain relationships with potential clients, including SME owners, entrepreneurs, and<br />\r\nbusiness professionals.<br />\r\nâ— Develop and maintain a strong pipeline of deals, meeting monthly and quarterly targets<br />\r\nâ— Conduct preliminary credit investigations to analyze applicants&rsquo; willingness and repayment capacity to<br />\r\ndetermine the feasibility of granting loans.<br />\r\nâ— Initiate and partner with reputable organizati