(102, 'Marketing Executive', 'Services', 'HND, BACHELOR', '1 - 3 years', '45', '', 'Lagos ', '', 'Full time', '1747246776_marketing exec_.png', 'Professional', '', '2025-06-14', '<p>The Marketing Executive will be responsible for driving local awareness, engagement, and revenue through strategic marketing initiatives across Lagos Island. This role focuses on promoting cinema operations, dining and catering services, and event spaces. The ideal candidate will use a mix of digital and traditional marketing tactics, social media campaigns, and grassroots outreach to build customer loyalty, generate sales, and grow the brand&#39;s visibility in the entertainment and hospitality space.</p>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Strong network within the film, cinema operations, hospitality, and distribution industries.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Demonstrated success in marketing, with a history of meeting or exceeding revenue goals.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>In-depth understanding of film distribution, cinema operations, and event marketing models.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Excellent communication, negotiation, and public presentation skills.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Strategic and creative thinking in partnership development and promotional planning.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Proficiency in CRM systems, Microsoft Office Suite, and proposal creation.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Passion for storytelling, entertainment, hospitality, and the film business.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Highly motivated and results-driven with a goal-oriented mindset.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Strong time management and multitasking skills with attention to detail.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>A collaborative team player able to work effectively across multiple departments.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><strong>Remuneration:</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Competitive Salary &amp; Performance-based Incentives</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><strong>Application:</strong></h3>\r\