(103, 'Online Marketers', 'Fintech', 'OND', '1 - 3 years', '45', '', 'Lagos ', '', 'Remote', '1748255431_online marketers-.png', 'Professional', '', '2025-06-30', '<p>The Online Marketer will play a pivotal role in growing the platform&rsquo;s vendor base by identifying and recruiting qualified wholesale vendors and artisans in high-demand categories. This role involves clearly communicating the platform&rsquo;s value proposition, guiding vendors through the onboarding process, and driving performance by implementing and optimizing digital outreach strategies. The ideal candidate is a proactive, persuasive, and tech-savvy individual with proven experience in digital marketing, vendor acquisition, and B2B sales.</p>\r\n', '<h3><strong>Qualifications &amp; Requirements:</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Minimum of <strong>ND (National Diploma)</strong> in Marketing, Business, Communications, or any relevant field.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>At least 2 years&rsquo; experience</strong> in online marketing, vendor acquisition, or B2B sales&mdash;preferably in the e-commerce sector.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Proficiency in digital marketing concepts, especially <strong>digital monetization models</strong> and <strong>value-based selling</strong>.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Strong ability to engage and convert vendors/artisans via digital platforms such as WhatsApp, forums, and online marketplaces.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Excellent persuasion, negotiation, and performance tracking skills.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Demonstrated <strong>self-motivation</strong>, adaptability, and results-oriented mindset.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Comfortable using digital productivity tools such as <strong>Google Workspace</strong>, <strong>CRM systems</strong>, and <strong>spreadsheets</strong>.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Identify and recruit qualified wholesale vendors an