(126, 'Outdoor Marketer', 'Banking & Finance', 'HND, BACHELOR', '1 - 3 years', '45', '', 'Lagos ', '', 'Full time', '1757439285_outdoor marketer - nora.jpg', 'Professional', '', '2025-10-11', '<p>The Outdoor Marketer will be responsible for driving sales growth through direct field marketing, lead generation, and customer engagement. This role involves representing the company as a brand ambassador at events, promoting offerings, and ensuring the achievement of sales targets while building long-term customer relationships.</p>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Marketing, Business Administration, or related field.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>3&ndash;5 years&rsquo; experience in real estate sales (domestic market).</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Strong communication, presentation, and negotiation skills.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Solid knowledge of the real estate market and financing options.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Familiarity with PMIs and ability to drive lead generation.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>CSP certification will be an added advantage.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Proactively identify and engage potential customers through face-to-face interactions, community outreach, and targeted field marketing campaigns.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Implement field sales strategies to achieve personal and team sales goals.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Professionally represent the company at promotional events, kiosks, and community gatherings to build brand awareness.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Present property offerings convincingly to potential clients, manage inquiries, handle initial complaints, and provide accurate product information.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Gather market intelligence by monitoring competitors&rsquo; activities and sharing insights with management.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Conduct weekly and monthly reports on field activities, lead generation, and client feedback for the He